Nicola Peltz has sparked a frenzy after revealing snaps of her latest hair transformation, leading her husband Brooklyn Beckham to give his nod of approval. The wife of Brooklyn, 27, posted a series of dazzling snaps of her newly-brunette tresses, after waving goodbye to her blonde locks. Posing in a striped shirt, Nicola showcased her brown hair which had been expertly styled around her heart-shaped face. The star captioned the sultry snap: "Back to my roots," alongside a wink face. Brooklyn was quick to give his wife's new tresses his stamp of approval, writing: "Sexy baby xxxxx."